nd Jade Mace. I have about 30k right now and am trying to decide if I should keep my FB and get a new main hand weapon or sell everything and get a Windblade. <br>
<br>
From the few things I have heard and read so far, the DPS on the windblade will be sufficient to keep and maintain aggro while doing a fair amount of damage, while the few combos I can afford for my level might do well for aggro but will be lacking in the DPS department.<br>
<br>
Also I am not sure if I will ever get to the point where I am MT in a guild.. maybe second or third.. Anyways, I would appreciate any suggestions you can provide. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=shadokastr>shadokastr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/2/03 6:27:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4772.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What weapons to purchase, 1hs or 2hs.</span><hr size=1> need more info hehe.  What level are you?  Whats your armor situation?  Where do you hunt?  Since i only hunt in the planes i would say 2hs all the way.  I have good aggro weaps and i never use them, they are always bagged for the Axe of dismay.  Repost damage hurts too much and it only gets worse as you go up in tiers.  So if ya plan to hunt in the planes go the 2h route.  Otherwise 1h is a hell of alot more aggro.  All depends on what you wanna do.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p>Nevian Shadowforge<br>
Myrmidon of Karana<br>
