~ RAH</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=brylden>Brylden</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/2/03 6:55:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4772.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What weapons to purchase, 1hs or 2hs.</span><hr size=1> Well right now I am only going to be duoing with a Cleric friend so it isn't that important right now, but when I hit 53 or so I plan to go straight to the planes. So I am wondering what would be best at 53ish or so.<br>
<br>
Another option that might be best is to keep my weapons and go for an Axe of Dismay and maybe a Snowchipper for my main hand? There are just too many options <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=167985">Brylden</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Level 56 Knight<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Innoruuk server<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://asylumofthefallen.com/">Asylum of the Fallen</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=carneab>Carne AB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/2/03 8:40:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4772.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What weapons to purchase, 1hs or 2hs.</span><hr size=1> you have only 1 option, windblade. It will outagro anything else that you can buy unless you get a lucky early proc from frosty. It is, as you stated, much better dps than anything else you will be considering. Definately worth picking up if you can. <p> &lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://spacefem.com/uselessquiz/index.shtml&quot;&gt;<br>
