&lt;a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=247012&gt; Vani Lala</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=trongstoutheart>trongstoutheart</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/2/03 9:11:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4772.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What weapons to purchase, 1hs or 2hs.</span><hr size=1> What about going with a Wavecrasher/Frosty combo? I think that might out agro a windblade, but thats just a guess.<br>
<br>
I have noticed that I do hold/pull pretty good agro with the two. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
